.TH "fsl_local_config_write" 9 "fsl_local_config_write" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
fsl_local_config_write \- Generate a MPC85xx local config space write
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" fsl_local_config_write
.BI "(struct rio_mport *mport "  ","
.BI "int index "  ","
.BI "u32 offset "  ","
.BI "int len "  ","
.BI "u32 data "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "mport" 12
RapidIO master port info
.IP "index" 12
ID of RapdiIO interface
.IP "offset" 12
Offset into configuration space
.IP "len" 12
Length (in bytes) of the maintenance transaction
.IP "data" 12
Value to be written
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Generates a MPC85xx local configuration space write. Returns 0 on
success or -EINVAL on failure.
